{"article_id":"pCQ5YIJhABJYgwek","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump on Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"gearing up for his first campaign rally in months in Tulsa , Oklahoma , on Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"threatened any protesters","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"who show up outside","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"or try to disrupt the event ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"\" it will be a much different scene \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"than how they 've been dealt with in `` New York , Seattle , or Minneapolis . ''","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` Any protesters , anarchists , agitators , looters or lowlifes","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who are going to Oklahoma","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"please understand ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"you will not be treated","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"like you have been in New York , Seattle , or Minneapolis .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"It will be a much different scene ! ''","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Trump tweeted Friday morning .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"It was n't clear exactly what Trump meant","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"or what he could do","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"to carry out his threat ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"but he has taken an increasingly hostile tone towards protesters in recent weeks ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"this time putting \" protesters \" in same category as \" anarchists \" \" looters \" and \" lowlifes . \"","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"He has blamed `` antifa '' for violence at protests , without evidence ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"and has repeatedly bragged about how the National Guard in Minneapolis dealt with protesters like a `` knife cutting butter . ''","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"A curfew was imposed","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"beginning Thursday night","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and into the weekend ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"according to Tulsa 's mayor ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"citing concerns abut organized groups","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"coming to the city .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"\" Last night , I enacted a curfew at the request of Tulsa Police Chief Wendell Franklin ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"following consultation with the United States Secret Service","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"based on intelligence","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"they had received , \"","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Mayor G.T . Bynum said in a statement ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"\" Today , we were told","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"the curfew is no longer necessary","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"so I am rescinding it . \"","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Trump tweeted ,","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"`` I just spoke to the highly respected Mayor of Tulsa , G.T . Bynum ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"who informed me","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"there will be no curfew tonight or tomorrow for our many supporters","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"attending the # MAGA Rally .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Enjoy yourselves -","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"thank you to Mayor Bynum !","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"President Donald Trump speaks during a roundtable with governors on the reopening of America 's small businesses , in the State Dining Room of the White House , June 18 , 2020 , in Washington .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Alex Brandon/AP","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"Trump 's rally was initially scheduled for Friday , June 19 ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"known as Juneteenth , the holiday","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"marking when the last people","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"who were still enslaved","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"were told","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"they were freed ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"more than two years after President Abraham Lincoln signed the Emancipation Proclamation .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"In a rare instance of his backing down under pressure ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"the president ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"after saying","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"he spoke with two black Secret Service agents ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"announced last week","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that he would reschedule the rally for the next day .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The city also is tense","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"because it 's the site of a race massacre in 1921","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"in which whites killed as many as 300 black residents .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Concerns of the rally go beyond race ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"as the state is still battling coronavirus","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"and has seen an recent uptick in cases .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Trump , in another tweet Friday , also said","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"he views his rally in Tulsa as the re-launch of his reelection campaign ,","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"saying ,","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"`` Big crowds and lines already forming in Tulsa .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"My campaign hasn ' t started yet .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"It starts on Saturday night in Oklahoma ! ''","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"The rally is expected to draw as many as 100,000 Trump supporters ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"some of whom had lined up outside the 19,000-seat Bank of Oklahoma Center in Tulsa , days before the rally .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Trump claimed this week","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"that over a million people had requested tickets for the event","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and his campaign has been exploring possible venues for an overflow crowd .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Supporters of President Donald Trump camp outside the BOK Center , the venue for his upcoming rally , in Tulsa , Oklahoma , June 17 , 2020 .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"Lawrence Bryant/Reuters","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Oklahoma 's Republican Gov . Kevin Stitt backed the rally","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"when he met with Trump at the White House Thursday at an unrelated event","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"focused on government assistance for small businesses .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Stitt assured","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"that the rally would be safe","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"even as the city ' s health official has called an event like the rally `` a huge risk factor ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"for spreading the coronavirus .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"\" It ' s a crowd like ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"I guess ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"nobody ' s seen before .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"We have tremendous , tremendous requests for tickets ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"I think ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"probably has never happened politically before , \"","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"bragging about the demand for tickets to his first rally amid the ongoing pandemic","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and telling Stitt","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"one of reasons","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"his campaign chose Oklahoma","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"was because the state has handled the pandemic \" incredibly well . \"","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"\" We 're so excited to have you , \"","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Stitt told Trump .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"\" And","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"like you said ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"if people caught that","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"but over a million people have requested tickets","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"to come","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"to come to this event","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"so it 's just gon na be amazing . \"","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Trump campaign spokesperson Erin Perrine told ABC News","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"the campaign `` takes the health and safety of rally-goers seriously","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"and is taking precautions","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"to make the rally safe , ''","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"including checking the temperatures of attendees","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and providing them with face masks and hand sanitizer .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":154,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":133,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":126,"right":132,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":119,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":116,"right":118,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":113,"right":115,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":2,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":5,"right":117,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":121,"right":123,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":120,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":13,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":128,"right":131,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":15,"right":127,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":129,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":146,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":14